'''肖恩·布倫特·克里斯坦'''（{{lang-en|Shawn Brent Christian }}；{{bd|1975年|9月14日}}），是一名[[皮特凯恩群岛|皮特凯恩群岛]]政治人物，現任[[皮特凱恩市長|皮特凱恩市長]]<ref>[http://www.demtullpitcairn.com/2013October.pdf Dem Tull] {{Wayback|url=http://www.demtullpitcairn.com/2013October.pdf |date=20140103232313 }} October 2013</ref>。

克里斯坦是前市長{{le|史蒂夫·克里斯坦|Steve Christian}}（Steve Christian）與奧利夫·祖·布朗（Olive Jal Brown）的兒子，並以父母朋友的兒子肖恩·布蘭尼根（Shawn Branigan）的名字肖恩取名<ref>[http://library.puc.edu/pitcairn/pitcairn/Pitcairners/ChristianMary.shtml Who Are the Pitcairners?] {{Wayback|url=http://library.puc.edu/pitcairn/pitcairn/Pitcairners/ChristianMary.shtml |date=20170524163356 }} Pitcairn Islands Study Center</ref>。他在1998年移居澳洲，並於[[新南威爾士州|新南威爾士州]][[纽卡斯尔_(新南威尔士州)|纽卡斯尔]]讀書<ref>[http://www.theage.com.au/news/World/Christian-challenges-Pitcairn-trial/2005/11/25/1132703348104.html Christian challenges Pitcairn trial] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theage.com.au/news/World/Christian-challenges-Pitcairn-trial/2005/11/25/1132703348104.html |date=20140411130305 }} The Age, 25 November 2005</ref><ref name=TA>[http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/nation/pitcairn-islander-guilty-of-child-sex/story-e6frg6nf-1111112807441 Pitcairn Islander guilty of child sex] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/nation/pitcairn-islander-guilty-of-child-sex/story-e6frg6nf-1111112807441 |date=20160604134408 }} The Australian, 10 January 2007</ref>。

他在2004年的{{le|2004年皮特凱恩性侵犯審判|Pitcairn sexual assault trial of 2004|皮特凱恩性侵犯審判}}也受父親和兄長蘭德爾（Randall）牽連，被引渡回新西蘭受審，被控強姦兒童及教唆強姦的兩項罪名<ref name=TA/>。其後克里斯坦被判處三年和半徒刑<ref>[http://www.rdasia.com/pitcairn_paradise_lost Pitcairn: Paradise Lost] {{Wayback|url=http://www.rdasia.com/pitcairn_paradise_lost |date=20140304172922 }} Readers Digest Asia</ref>，但入獄兩年後獲釋<ref>[http://www.independent.co.uk/environment/green-living/ecotourism-pitcairn-strives-to-live-down-its-terrible-past-2192004.html Eco-tourism: Pitcairn strives to live down its terrible past] The Independent</ref>
。

